code:
graph TD
    subgraph "Tree Detection"
        PLR[FinTech_AuthVault] --> SCAN[FinTech_FraudDetection]
        SCAN --> LOGS[FinTech_AuthVault]
        LOGS --> CLUSTER[FinTech_FraudDetection]
        CLUSTER --> BASE[FinTech_LedgerService]
        BASE --> CHECK{FinTech_LedgerService}
        CHECK -->|No| ADD[FinTech_LedgerService]
        CHECK -->|Yes| SKIP[FinTech_LedgerService]
        ADD --> TREES[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    end
    
    subgraph "Tree Cutting Process"
        REQ[FinTech_TransactionQueue] --> LLM[FinTech_FraudDetection]
        LLM --> COORD[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
        COORD --> MOVE[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
        MOVE --> START[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
        
        START --> HEIGHT[FinTech_AuthVault]
        HEIGHT --> FINDLOGS[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
        FINDLOGS --> HASLOG{FinTech_LedgerService}
        
        HASLOG -->|Yes| CUT[FinTech_FraudDetection]
        HASLOG -->|No| NEXTH[FinTech_AuthVault]
        
        CUT --> EFFECTS[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
        EFFECTS --> WOOD[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
        WOOD --> MORE{FinTech_PaymentGateway}
        
        MORE -->|Yes| HEIGHT
        MORE -->|No| NEXTH
        
        NEXTH --> MAXH{FinTech_TransactionQueue}
        MAXH -->|No| HEIGHT
        MAXH -->|Yes| DONE[FinTech_LedgerService]
        
        DONE --> MARK[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
        MARK --> COMPLETE[FinTech_LedgerService]
    end
    
    subgraph "Cut Tree Registry"
        MARK --> REGISTRY[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
        REGISTRY --> KEY[FinTech_FraudDetection]
        KEY --> PERSIST[FinTech_FraudDetection]
        PERSIST --> PREVENT[FinTech_FraudDetection]
    end
    
    style SCAN fill:#e8f5e8
    style CUT fill:#ffebee
    style EFFECTS fill:#fff3e0
    style REGISTRY fill:#f3e5f5
repo_description: Intelligent Agentic NPCs for Minecraft with LLM Integration
